com.ibm.mashups.enabler.services
Interface ConfigConstants

public ConfigConstants

This constants class contains well defined constants available to the config service. They are defined in the ConfigService.properties

PERSISTENCE_MODE

unknown PERSISTENCE_MODE
Defines the persistence mode that should be used by the iContext. Default is DOM.

PERSISTENCE_MODE_EVENTS

unknown PERSISTENCE_MODE_EVENTS
Defines the read-only persistence mode for the event provider that is used by the iContext. It overwrites any mode defined as part of PERSISTENCE_MODE.Default is DOM.

PERSISTENCE_MODE_EVENTS_MODIFIABLE

unknown PERSISTENCE_MODE_EVENTS_MODIFIABLE
Defines the modifiable persistence mode for the event provider that is used by the iContext. It overwrites any mode defined as part of PERSISTENCE_MODE.Default is DOM.

PERSISTENCE_MODE_WIRES

unknown PERSISTENCE_MODE_WIRES
Defines the read-only persistence mode for the wire provider that is used by the iContext. It overwrites any mode defined as part of PERSISTENCE_MODE.Default is DOM.

PERSISTENCE_MODE_WIRES_MODIFIABLE

unknown PERSISTENCE_MODE_WIRES_MODIFIABLE
Defines the modifiable persistence mode for the wire provider that is used by the iContext. It overwrites any mode defined as part of PERSISTENCE_MODE.Default is DOM.

PERSISTENCE_MODE_ATTRIBUTES

unknown PERSISTENCE_MODE_ATTRIBUTES
Defines the read-only persistence mode for the attributes provider that is used by the iContext. It overwrites any mode defined as part of PERSISTENCE_MODE.Default is DOM.

PERSISTENCE_MODE_ATTRIBUTES_MODIFIABLE

unknown PERSISTENCE_MODE_ATTRIBUTES_MODIFIABLE
Defines the modifiable persistence mode for the attributes provider that is used by the iContext. It overwrites any mode defined as part of PERSISTENCE_MODE.Default is DOM.

PERSISTENCE_MODE_ATTRIBUTES_JSON_INJECTXML

unknown PERSISTENCE_MODE_ATTRIBUTES_JSON_INJECTXML
Defines whether the json attributes implementation will be injecting the attributes defined in the widget xml as well into the attributes map. This will only apply if the json attributes have been enabled through the PERSISTENCE_MODE_ATTRIBUTES setting.

ICONTEXT_AUTO_COMMIT

unknown ICONTEXT_AUTO_COMMIT
Defines whether autocommit is enabled on the iContext. If set to true the iContext will automatically commit data to the backend if commit is called on e.g. the iWidgetAttributes.
